Papaya Boat (tropical salad bowl):
My favourite easy go to fruit salad bowl. Start by slicing the papaya into two halves, next add a thick layer of greek yoghurt and add your favourite tropical fruits inside the papaya bowl. Season with nuts and dry seeds and you’re good to go!
